{"tid":396264,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個日本旅行時遇到/見到既痴漢實錄","createTime":"2017-09-11T14:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-13T10:54:43.000Z","uid":72444,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"449d79de3f59ff3f5f1bdc95d060df25a7ad6a78","tid":396264,"uid":72444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:04:07.000Z","msg":"當時自己一個去左富士河口湖玩幾日<br />\n租左架單車諗住環湖一周<br />\n踩踩下有架私家車跟住我<br />\n然後佢停低左係我隔離<br />\n<br />\n佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：天氣咁熱 不如上我架車啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔洗喇 唔該哂你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔緊要啦 我車你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔洗喇 我有架單車 唔方便<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你將架單車泊埋一二邊啦 我架車好涼<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔洗喇 唔該<br />\n<br />\n開頭以為日本人咁nice <br />\n但發覺佢講野果陣唔係望住我對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後擾攘左一陣 我拎部電話出黎佢先肯走<br />\n各位巴絲有無見過或者遇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a43f96f2d29df3836b603450baf2d64547a9499","tid":396264,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"你係男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95f9c8ec7c339d9fb84b423be772f9b9ccafffa","tid":396264,"uid":8435,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"喺月台排隊上車，前面個男人拎份報紙出嚟<br />\n無啦啦伸長條脷喺度不停奶<br />\n仲要嗰版唔係咩女優，只係個廣告，有一大塊草原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c5e0e9f49d3824484865c6af50f4e4e3f4ce6f","tid":396264,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"姐係望你對波？"},{"pid":"ed169c2286629fa6a189ed92c94029b730ca402a","tid":396264,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"你未講你係男定女.."},{"pid":"2fdcbe80ed96034bca6922c38e930a9a9bcd47cc","tid":396264,"uid":15236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"望住你條jer？"},{"pid":"b44c304253fe66ac035afe5063bd02747d370b6e","tid":396264,"uid":72444,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係望你對波？</blockquote><br />\n望住我迷人既胸肌<br />\n以及漲卜卜既褲浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d7e6d8da89aafd9be63bb3671ad3454f4e7d3c","tid":396264,"uid":37131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb00a9421644a858512b746d5dc8ca42e8004d65","tid":396264,"uid":72444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嘩 夜晚真係小心d<br />\n有次條街得我同個醉酒佬<br />\n佢不斷係到嗌:ねね ねね<br />\n我頭也不回咁跑番hostel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30716cd1a6ce7c72769b2d2cdc460b8c7140fcb","tid":396264,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"試過係箱根浸溫泉時俾人雞姦⋯"},{"pid":"59683b50a8cc10a808901cd4770c3fb38b6df45c","tid":396264,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過係箱根浸溫泉時俾人雞姦⋯</blockquote><br />\n......"},{"pid":"ccce705df7e8e77ff28113110dfee6f95cd3fbdc","tid":396264,"uid":78559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過係箱根浸溫泉時俾人雞姦⋯</blockquote><br />\n......</blockquote><br />\n........."},{"pid":"4ccb8d0721df2fe